sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MutatingWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ValidatingWH as Validating Webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RayClusterCtrl as RayCluster Controller
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS:6379 Dashboard:8265 Client:10001
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Redis as External Redis<br/>6379/TCP Optional mTLS

    Note over User,Redis: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI->>MutatingWH: Admission Request<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Kubernetes admission
    MutatingWH-->>K8sAPI: Mutated RayCluster<br/>Default configs + security
    K8sAPI->>ValidatingWH: Validation Request<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Kubernetes admission
    ValidatingWH-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayCluster Created

    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayClusterCtrl: RayCluster Event
    RayClusterCtrl->>CertMgr: Create Certificate CRs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    CertMgr-->>RayClusterCtrl: Certificates Created
    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod, Services<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayHead: Pod Scheduled
    RayClusterCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayWorker: Pods Scheduled

    RayWorker->>RayHead: Register with GCS<br/>6379/TCP Redis<br/>Optional mTLS
    RayHead->>Redis: GCS Fault Tolerance<br/>6379/TCP Optional TLS<br/>Password auth

    Note over User,Redis: Flow 2: RayJob Submission

    participant Client as Ray Client
    participant RayJobCtrl as RayJob Controller

    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayJob Created
    RayJobCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayJobCtrl: RayJob Event
    RayJobCtrl->>Client: Submit Job<br/>10001/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional mTLS
    Client->>RayHead: Job Request<br/>6379/TCP Redis<br/>Optional mTLS
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Distribute Tasks<br/>Dynamic Ray Protocol<br/>Optional mTLS
    RayWorker-->>RayHead: Task Results
    RayHead-->>Client: Job Complete
    Client-->>RayJobCtrl: Job Status
    RayJobCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update RayJob Status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)

    Note over User,Redis: Flow 3: RayService Model Serving

    participant ExtClient as External Client
    participant Ingress as Ingress/Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant RayServe as Ray Serve Service<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant RayServiceCtrl as RayService Controller

    ExtClient->>Ingress: POST /predict<br/>Auth: Optional Bearer
    Ingress->>RayServe: Forward Request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP<br/>Optional TLS
    RayServe->>RayWorker: Execute Prediction<br/>Dynamic Ray Protocol<br/>Optional mTLS
    RayWorker-->>RayServe: Prediction Result
    RayServe-->>Ingress: Response
    Ingress-->>ExtClient: JSON Response

    RayServiceCtrl->>K8sAPI: Monitor Service Health<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    K8sAPI-->>RayServiceCtrl: Service Status

    Note over User,Redis: Flow 4: Operator Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant Operator as kuberay-operator<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Prometheus->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP No Auth
    Operator-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics
